data.description: Great location! Beautiful 3 bedrooms, 3 bath home, attached one car garage sitting on 2 acres at the edge of town with 2 living areas. formal dining room, wood burning fireplace, patio area, large, paved driveway, sidewalks, barn w/ loft (1080 sq.ft.) plus a detached 1 car garage (420 sq.ft) mature trees, pond, partial pipe fencing and located in a quiet neighborhood. Motivated Sellers!!
